| HistoryText             = The Defenders originated after the superheroes of [[Warp World]] were rallied by [[Emma Frost (Earth-616)|Emma Frost]] to fight the soul-consuming [[Devondra (Earth-616)|Devondra]]. Following Devondra's defeat, and the restoration of [[Earth-616]] while keeping Warp World intact, some of these heroes, namely [[Stephen Rogers (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Soldier Supreme]], [[Stark Odinson (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Iron Hammer]], [[Peter Parker (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Arachknight]] and [[Laura Kinney (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Weapon Hex]], decided to remain together, and formed the Defenders, a group of protectors of Warp World.{{r|Infinity Wars Vol 1 6}}
